message.content: The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are "cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.DB". The paper deals with natural language question answering over knowledge bases, which involves aspects of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), and databases (cs.DB). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
